<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Backups - Jellyfin Companion Admin">
  <title>Backups - Jellyfin Companion</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/fontawesome.css">
  <style>
    /* Stats Grid */
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: white;
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-md);
    }
    .stat-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .stat-icon.primary { background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1); color: var(--primary); }
    .stat-icon.success { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); color: var(--success); }
    .stat-icon.warning { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); color: var(--warning); }
    .stat-content h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .stat-content p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    /* Quick Actions */
    .actions-card {
      background: white;
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    .actions-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
    .actions-card h3 i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .action-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }
    .info-box {
      background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.05);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .info-box i {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-right: var(--spacing-xs);
    }

    /* Backups Table */
    .table-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    .table-card-header {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .table-card-header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
    .table-card-header h3 i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .backups-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .backups-table th {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .backups-table td {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .backups-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .backups-table tr:hover {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
    }
    .backup-name {
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }
    .backup-size {
      font-family: monospace;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .backup-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--spacing-xs);
    }

    /* Empty State */
    .empty-state {
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-lg);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .empty-state i {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      color: var(--gray-300);
    }
    .empty-state h3 {
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm) 0;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }
    .empty-state p {
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Info Section */
    .info-section {
      background: white;
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .info-section h4 {
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
    .info-section h4 i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .info-section ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .info-section code {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
    }

    /* Notification */
    .notification {
      position: fixed;
      top: var(--spacing-lg);
      right: var(--spacing-lg);
      padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-lg);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      z-index: 1001;
      transform: translateX(150%);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .notification.show {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    .notification.success {
      background: var(--success);
      color: white;
    }
    .notification.error {
      background: var(--danger);
      color: white;
    }

    /* Modal */
    .modal-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 1000;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .modal-overlay.active {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
    }
    .modal {
      background: white;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transform: scale(0.9);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .modal-overlay.active .modal {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    .modal-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }
    .modal-header.warning {
      background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
    }
    .modal-header.warning i {
      color: var(--warning);
    }
    .modal-header.danger {
      background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    }
    .modal-header.danger i {
      color: var(--danger);
    }
    .modal-header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }
    .modal-body {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    .modal-body p {
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .backup-name-display {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .modal-footer {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--spacing-sm);
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .backup-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-container">
    <%- include('../partials/navigation', { user, currentPage: 'admin-backups' }) %>
    <main class="main-content">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
          <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" id="mobileMenuToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
            <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
          </button>
          <h1 class="header-title">Backups
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
          <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" id="refreshBtn">
            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Refresh
          </button>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="page-content">
        <!-- Notification -->
        <div id="notification" class="notification"></div>

        <!-- Stats Cards -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon primary">
              <i class="fas fa-archive"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-content">
              <h3><%= backups ? backups.length : 0 %></h3>
              <p>Total Backups</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon success">
              <i class="fas fa-hdd"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-content">
              <h3><%= totalSize %></h3>
              <p>Total Size</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon warning">
              <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-content">
              <h3><%= latestBackupDate %></h3>
              <p>Latest Backup</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Actions -->
        <div class="actions-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Quick Actions</h3>
          <div class="action-buttons">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="createBackupBtn">
              <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Create Backup
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
            Backups are automatically created on a schedule. You can manually create one now or restore from an existing backup below.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Backups Table -->
        <div class="table-card">
          <div class="table-card-header">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-list"></i> Available Backups</h3>
            <span class="badge"><%= backups ? backups.length : 0 %> files</span>
          </div>
          <% if (backups && backups.length > 0) { %>
            <table class="backups-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Date</th>
                  <th>File Name</th>
                  <th>Size</th>
                  <th>Actions</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <% backups.forEach((backup, index) => { %>
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <div style="font-weight: 600;"><%= new Date(backup.date).toLocaleDateString() %></div>
                      <div style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-secondary);"><%= new Date(backup.date).toLocaleTimeString() %></div>
                    </td>
                    <td><code class="backup-name"><%= backup.name %></code></td>
                    <td class="backup-size"><%= backup.size %></td>
                    <td>
                      <div class="backup-actions">
                        <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm" data-action="download" data-backup="<%= backup.name %>" title="Download">
                          <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn btn-warning btn-sm" data-action="restore" data-backup="<%= backup.name %>" title="Restore">
                          <i class="fas fa-undo"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" data-action="delete" data-backup="<%= backup.name %>" title="Delete">
                          <i class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                        </button>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% }); %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          <% } else { %>
            <div class="empty-state">
              <i class="fas fa-inbox"></i>
              <h3>No Backups Found</h3>
              <p>Create your first backup using the button above</p>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Info Section -->
        <div class="info-section">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Backup Information</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Backups are stored in the <code>backups/</code> directory</li>
            <li>Automatic backups are created according to your maintenance schedule</li>
            <li>Manual backups can be created using the "Create Backup" button</li>
            <li>Restoring a backup will replace the current database with the backup version</li>
            <li>Current database is backed up before restoration as a safety measure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <!-- Restore Modal -->
  <div id="restoreModal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal">
      <div class="modal-header warning">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        <h3>Restore Database</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Are you sure you want to restore from this backup?</p>
        <p><strong>Warning:</strong> This will replace your current database. Your current database will be backed up first.</p>
        <div id="restoreBackupName" class="backup-name-display"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-action="close-modal">Cancel</button>
        <button class="btn btn-warning" id="confirmRestoreBtn">
          <i class="fas fa-undo"></i> Restore
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Delete Modal -->
  <div id="deleteModal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal">
      <div class="modal-header danger">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
        <h3>Delete Backup</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Are you sure you want to delete this backup?</p>
        <p><strong>This action cannot be undone.</strong></p>
        <div id="deleteBackupName" class="backup-name-display"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-action="close-modal">Cancel</button>
        <button class="btn btn-danger" id="confirmDeleteBtn">
          <i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Delete
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/mobile-nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/admin-backups.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/admin-dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
